msgstr "表達式無效"

#: find/tree.c:126
#, c-format
msgid "invalid expression; you have used a binary operator '%s' with nothing before it."
msgstr "表達式無效：您在前面沒有任何內容的情況下使用了二元運算元「%s」。"

#: find/tree.c:135 find/tree.c:194
#, c-format
